{"tid":1022460,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"喉嚨唔痛","createTime":"2019-02-15T04:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T12:17:20.000Z","uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee7c665c32b82d3ec99959c532729c71e95066f6","tid":1022460,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:54:51.000Z","msg":"早排先鼻敏發作...睇個濕尻醫生好左少少<br />\n之後KEEP仕都係有鼻水咁<br />\n<br />\n前幾日又返發咁<br />\n拎左個濕尻醫生既藥袋去藥房配藥<br />\n屌佢老味消炎同收鼻水各10粒都係廿蚊雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食到前日鼻水都禁唔住,逢訓覺訓著左 D鼻水就啪啪聲咁湧<br />\n卒之搞到呢家狀況係夜晚訓得著,訓訓下會醒,咳兩咳又繼續訓,然後朝早一起身就勁咳,直到咳哂D綠痰出黎同清極都係FEEL到仲有痰<br />\n<strong>咳到仲有陣維他奶味</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但仆你個街喉嚨又唔痛,鼻水又呻極都係蘿蔔絲咁少<br />\n<br />\n究竟乜病黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929ff652558091efd82881e0e0dcab58b4f29945","tid":1022460,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"></span>"}]}